{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 44547599, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "SMP-COSME-2021-TOURSME-01", "title": "COVID-19 Recovery Through Sustainable Tourism Growth and SME Support", "publicationDateLong": 1639008000000, "callIdentifier": "SMP-COSME-2021-TOURSME", "callTitle": "COVID-19 Recovery Through Sustainable Tourism Growth and SME Support", "callccm2Id": 44547615, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "workProgrammepart": {"id": 286550, "ccm_id": 43469376, "wp_part": "SMP-2021", "wp_year": "SMP-2021", "wp_title": "SMP-2021", "wp_website": "https://ec.europa.eu/competition-policy/single-market-programme-smp_en", "wp_document": "https://ec.europa.eu/competition-policy/single-market-programme-smp_en"}, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43252476, "abbreviation": "SMP", "description": "Single Market Programme (SMP)"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 43252504, "abbreviation": "Cosme", "description": "Cosme"}], "topicMGAs": [], "tags": ["COVID-19", "Sustainable Growth", "Tourism", "SME Support", "innovation hubs", "incubators", "tourism value chain", "digital and green transformation", "accelerators", "Recovery", "tourism  ecosystem industry stakeholders"], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "SMP-GFS SMP Grants for Financial Support", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43250793, "abbreviation": "SMP-AG", "description": "SMP Action Grant Budget-Based"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "09 December 2021", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["02 March 2022"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3373086": [{"action": "SMP-COSME-2021-TOURSME-01 - SMP-GFS SMP Grants for Financial Support", "plannedOpeningDate": "09 December 2021", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["02 March 2022"], "budgetYearMap": {"2021": 12420000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2021"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">ExpectedOutcome</SPAN>:<p><strong>Expected results:</strong></p><ul level=\"0\"><li>Enhanced resilience and competitiveness of tourism SMEs through better uptake of sustainability principles, innovation, and digitalisation (i.e. use of new technologies, greening, data);</li><li>New business models in tourism building on digitalisation, new technologies, sustainability, circularity;</li><li>Enhanced cooperation along the tourism value chain;</li><li>Improved transnational and cross-border cooperation, knowledge transfer and peer learning;</li><li>Support to recovery of the tourism ecosystem from COVID-19 crisis by providing best practices for recovery investment.</li> </ul>\n<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p><strong>Scope:</strong></p><p>This call for proposals will be part of the overall COVID-19 recovery strategy for a sustainable tourism ecosystem and remain in line with the priorities of SME strategy and industrial strategy.</p><p>This action is to guide the recovery of the tourism ecosystem by providing support, including with the intermediary of consortia of organisations of the relevant tourism industry stakeholders, to the digital and green transformation of tourism companies, particularly SMEs, and boosting innovation, resilience, sustainability and quality along the tourism value chain.</p><p>The activity will also include provision of financial support to third parties, e.g. SMEs.</p>\n", "conditions": "<p><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">1.<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;bold\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Eligible countries</span></b><span style=\"font-size:&#10;9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">:&nbsp;as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/smp/wp-call/2021/call-fiche_smp-cosme-2021-toursme_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; Eligibility and admissibility conditions:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/smp/wp-call/2021/call-fiche_smp-cosme-2021-toursme_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">P</span></strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">roposal page limits and layout:</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Please refer to Part B of the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/smp/temp-form/af/af_smp-cosme_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">standard proposal template</a>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; Evaluation:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Evaluation criteria, scoring, threshold and process are described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/smp/wp-call/2021/call-fiche_smp-cosme-2021-toursme_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; Indicative timetable for evaluation and grant agreement:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/smp/wp-call/2021/call-fiche_smp-cosme-2021-toursme_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp; Proposal templates, guidance and model grant agreements (MGA):</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/smp/temp-form/af/af_smp-cosme_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Standard proposal template</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/smp/wp-call/2021/call-fiche_smp-cosme-2021-toursme_en.p