lank\">Single Market Programme establishment act</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>", "supportInfo": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">For help related to this </span><b style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">call</b><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">, please contact:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(198, 219, 239); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.6px;\">eismea-smp-cosme-enquiries@ec.europa.eu&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/faq;grantAndTendertype=1;categories=p_submission_eval;programme=null;actions=;keyword=;period=null\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Funding &amp; Tenders Portal FAQ</span></a><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> &ndash; Submission of proposals.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/helpdesks/contact-form\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">IT Helpdesk</span></a><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> &ndash; Contact the IT helpdesk for questions such as forgotten passwords, access rights and roles, technical aspects of submission of proposals, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/om_en.pdf\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Online Manual</span></a><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> &ndash; Please be aware that the Manual is currently drafted for the H2020 Programme and may not entirely fit for other programmes. However, a revision is being completed to make it corporate.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><a href=\"http://een.ec.europa.eu/\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Enterprise Europe Network</span></a><b><u><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0088CC;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> </span></u></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&ndash;</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Contact your Network national contact for advice to business with special focus on SMEs. The support includes guidance on EU research funding.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span><a href=\"http://www.iprhelpdesk.eu/\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Intellectual Property Helpdesk</span></a> <span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&ndash; Contact the IP Helpdesk for advice on the IP elements of your grant agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"staticAdditionalInfo": "<p><strong>Total amount of the action</strong>: EUR 12,420,0000</p><p><strong>Rate of co-financing:</strong> The co-financing rate shall be up to 100% of the eligible costs for financial support to third parties and up to 90% of the eligible costs for all other cost categories.</p>\n", "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Jan 21, 2022 4:02:32 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jan 21, 2022 4:02:32 PM", "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:navy;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">An updated version (Version 2.0) of the Call has been published on the 21<sup>st</sup> January 2022. </span><span style=\"color:#1F497D\">The changes are listed in &lsquo;History of Changes&rsquo; on Page 2 of the Call, and relate to text in yellow. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:#1F497D\">One of these changes concerns the Call deadline, which has been extended to the 2<sup>nd</sup> March, 2022 (17 hours, Brussels time).<o:p></o:p></span></p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Jan 13, 2022 2:33:34 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jan 13, 2022 2:33:34 PM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: SMP-COSME-2021-TOURSME-01(SMP-GFS)"}, {"approvalDate": "Dec 9, 2021 12:00:00 AM", "lastChangeDate": "Dec 9, 2021 12:00:00 AM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: SMP-COSME-2021-TOURSME-01(SMP-GFS)"}], "hasForthcomingTopics": false, "hasOpenTopics": false, "allClosedTopics": true}}}